{"tid":1613431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅持五大訴求 升級獨立調查為重組警隊","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T18:02:25.000Z","uid":249705,"like":41,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"23ba9c9028da6c92f8fc1d1f8e0ed4a763136b14","tid":1613431,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:13:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n5 demands, not one less.<br />\n<br />\n1)全面撤回送中惡法<br />\nThe complete withdrawal of the proposed extradition bill<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2)落實行政長官及立法會雙普選<br />\nGenuine universal suffrage for Chief Executive and Legislative Council</span><br />\n<br />\n3)撤回對民主運動暴動定性<br />\nWithdraw the use of the word &ldquo;riot&rdquo; in relation to democratic protests<br />\n<br />\n4)無條件釋放抗爭者 撤銷相關控罪<br />\nUnconditional release of arrested protesters and drop charges against them<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">5)追究警方濫權 重組警隊<br />\nCall to account police abuse of power, restructure the Police Force</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解要訴求升級做重組警隊? 獨立調查唔夠?<br />\nA: 多月嚟嘅警方濫權行為顯示香港警隊結構性失效，已經冇個別警員能夠為警隊濫權問題負責。根據民間記者會喺9月初收集超過13萬名市民嘅意見，要求重組警隊獲得嘅<span style=\"color: teal;\">支持度超過8成6</span>。因此，只有通過<span style=\"color: teal;\">民主政府</span>重組警隊結構，先可以從<span style=\"color: teal;\">根本</span>解決警隊濫權問題，重建警隊國際聲譽，恢復市民信任。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解唔升級做六大訴求?<br />\nA: 重組警隊及成立獨立調查委員會同樣係針對警隊濫權問題，而且必須先追究警察濫權問題，至可以真正重組警隊，因此可以歸納為同一項。另外「五大訴求 缺一不可」口號已經深入民心，<span style=\"color: teal;\">更改口號對本地及國際支持都可能有負面影響</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家認同嘅話，請全力開始做文宣。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"949d50ee046f14ad1eab8dec42dfb6f576f30d16","tid":1613431,"uid":249705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"重組警隊 刻不容緩！"},{"pid":"e46dedba37b1215e409eee6ee2c2f738a85366cb","tid":1613431,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"再唔還錢起你釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你咪起囉我都無諗過還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6328e29b7159c632589ea2ff9a4094318f59109c","tid":1613431,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"五大 係五大！<br />\n唔轉 只係升級"},{"pid":"0e0eef7b168c129a1a049626f23cab37f0625529","tid":1613431,"uid":249705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e46dedba37b1215e409eee6ee2c2f738a85366cb","tid":1613431,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"再唔還錢起你釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你咪起囉我都無諗過還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"中國人的性情是總喜歡調和、折中的。譬如你說，這個屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不容許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開窗了。沒有更激烈的主張，他們總連平和的改革也不肯行。&rdquo; <br />\n-魯迅<br />\n<br />\n手足用條命嚟換咗一次升級嘅機會<br />\n既然有國際輿論壓力 點解唔捉緊機會?<br />\n<br />\n而且開咗實彈都唔升級<br />\n唔通由得佢哋繼續開槍?"},{"pid":"f6118707cf3ed79b1000b9401356c004944c11a9","tid":1613431,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6328e29b7159c632589ea2ff9a4094318f59109c","tid":1613431,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"五大 係五大！<br />\n唔轉 只係升級"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:20:54.000Z","msg":"冇錯 貿貿然變做六大訴求 好難聽"},{"pid":"42dc48696d3fa52a3e8e556bcb96df82df3e3e21","tid":1613431,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b8ea327c543751dbb9585f33aa3ba0b8c37dd8c1","tid":1613431,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f72f45ef1a547bd989554132d0afe0109b9443d","tid":1613431,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited